data.description: This immaculate two story home offers a high end master bathroom remodel including an extended  walk-in ceramic tile shower, garden tub and dual vanities.  On top of that, all the lighting has been upgraded, the ceiling fans are all Harbor Breeze brand and high end 2 inch genuine wood blinds for the windows.  The home includes top tier laminate wood floors, upgraded black appliances, and tile backsplash. The living room has flat screen wiring and mounts already in place. The 2nd living upstairs could easily be converted to a 4th bedroom to add value and living accommodations. Enjoy your premium lot upgrade with a custom built high quality floating 12x18 wood deck.  This home is move in ready.
